### 所有请求都带上uid参数,并且header中带上 Authorization:token
@url = http://localhost:8895

### 1️⃣ 新增音乐
POST {{url}}/app/music/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uid": 1,
  "cover_url": "https://example.com/cover.jpg",
  "song_name": "Example Song",
  "artist_name": "Example Artist",
  "isrc": "US1234567890",
  "music_link": "https://example.com/music.mp3"
}

### 2️⃣ 获取音乐详情
GET {{url}}/app/music/get?id=1

