### 3️⃣ 更新音乐信息
PUT {{url}}/app/music/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "song_name": "Updated Song Name",
  "artist_name": "Updated Artist",
  "music_link": "https://example.com/updated_music.mp3"
}

### 4️⃣ 删除音乐
DELETE {{url}}/app/music/delete?id=1

### 5️⃣ 获取音乐列表（分页）
GET {{url}}/app/music/list?page=1&size=10

